name: Haunted House (The Dark Destiny from SPAN Ministries) in Tallmadge, Ohio.ogv

desc.html: This image is from an act from The Dark Destiny production by The 4:12 of S.P.A.N. (Shepherd's Pasture For All Nations) Ministries of Tallmadge, Ohio. This event took place on the weekend before Halloween in October 2013. Similar to the goals of Judgement House, The Dark Destiny was described as "a series of dramatic events, acted out by dedicated and talented college students to show observers how decisions and lifestyle choices can mean the difference between life and death." Free shuttles were provided from the student center of Kent State University to the event at The First Church of God in the Tallmadge/Kent area.
